</pre></div><h2 id=3D"characteristics-of-the-adjacency-list"><span>Characte=
ristics of the Adjacency List:</span></h2><ul><li value=3D"1"><span>An adja=
cency list representation uses a list of lists. We store all adjacent of ev=
ery node together.</span></li><li value=3D"2"><span>The size of the list is=
 determined by the number of vertices in the graph.</span></li><li value=3D=
