nt, we need only O(n) time where is the number of adjacent vertices.</span>=
</li></ul><h2 id=3D"applications-of-the-adjacency-list"><span>Applications =
of the Adjacency List:</span></h2><ul><li value=3D"1"><a href=3D"https://ww=
w.geeksforgeeks.org/dsa/introduction-to-graphs-data-structure-and-algorithm=
-tutorials/" rel=3D"noopener"><span>Graph algorithms</span></a><span>: Many=
 graph algorithms like </span><a href=3D"https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/dsa/=
