<span>Breadth First Search</span></a><span>, and </span><a href=3D"https://=
www.geeksforgeeks.org/dsa/depth-first-search-or-dfs-for-a-graph/" rel=3D"no=
opener"><span>Depth First Search</span></a><span> perform faster for adjace=
ncy lists to represent graphs.</span></li><li value=3D"2"><span>Adjacency L=
ist representation is the most commonly used representation of graph as it =
allows easy traversal of all edges.</span></li></ul><h2 id=3D"advantages-of=
-using-an-adjacency-list"><span>Advantages of using an Adjacency list:</spa=
n></h2><ul><li value=3D"1"><span>An adjacency list is simple and easy to un=
